@STANDARDS
- 5 universal rules (NEVER violate):
  1. Background ONLY from colors.navy[X]
  2. Text fontWeight >= 500, color from purple[50/100/200/300]
  3. Accent ONLY blue[400] (UI) or purple[600] (CTA)
  4. Use glow.* instead of boxShadow rgba(0,0,0,...)
  5. Animations ONLY through springs.* and timing.* presets
- NEVER hardcode hex outside tokens.ts
- Always import branded components from src/components/
- Default background: SpiralGalaxy (canvas galaxy ~6000 stars)
- Layer order: SpiralGalaxy → LiquidGlassPanel → children → TopBar → Watermark
- 152 branded components, 10 templates, 6 hooks
